data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER. A rare find in Central! Beautifully remodeled 3 bedrooms 2.5 bath home in the established neighborhood of Bellingrath Estates near the Central Thruway. Come take a look and you will feel welcomed by the entry deck, then step into the huge great room with beamed vaulted ceilings, wet bar, custom bookshelves and entertainment center and a fantastic view of your very private back yard. The beautiful eat in kitchen has custom cabinets, granite counter tops, tons of storage, and all new appliances. Off the kitchen, you have access to the laundry room, a half bath, patio, and formal dining room. The spacious master bedroom features a beautifully tiled master bath and vanity area, his and hers walk-in closets with barn doors, and access to the hot tub area and deck. Additional bedrooms are large with walk-in closets and picturesque windows. This home has newer thermal pane windows, flooring, and paint throughout the entire house. If you like a bright and light home with loads of storage and backyard privacy, you will love this home! The outdoor space boasts almost ½ acre with a large entertaining patio, fully fenced in back yard with electronic gate, two-car carport, AND a 24x24 shop/garage with a roll-up garage door, 50 amp 2-pole power, AC and fully insulated. Also has additional space for your boat or camper with 30 amp power supply off the garage. This one will not last long. Schedule your showing today!
